pageContext.claim: “Cuomo has weaponized the prosecutors to do his dirty work (and to keep him out of jams), a reason some don't want to be... ....in New York, and another reason they are leaving.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump with no evidence suggests New York state prosecutors are keeping Gov. Andrew Cuomo (D) out of "jams." The state attorney general, who is elected independently of the governor in New York, successfully sued Trump for violating several laws in the running of his charitable foundation. Trump settled the case.
